Finally, after crazy amount of work, I'm proud to announce release of PHP CS Fixer v2.0.0.

~250 PR were created to bring better experience. Dozens of new Fixers, possibility to easy configure them, great performance boost (including dedicated solutions just for PHP 7), full support of PHP 7.0 syntax and better integration with CIs are waiting for you!
Before usage be sure to check out our [UPGRADE](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/blob/v2.0.0/UPGRADE.md) guide and [README](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/blob/v2.0.0/README.rst).
